    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 1 Minute</p></div><p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require 0.2 pounds of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.fnmCUzOkiNZDOpQ0]{pure holy silver and iron powder} (one quarter sterling silver, three quarters iron), typically valued at 25 gold. You can alternatively use a pound of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.IndrcQ3rdMXvfyVh]{holy water} to sanctify a weapon. This spell consumes this material.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong>Enchant Item</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">You touch a weapon. That weapon counts as a &amp;reference[silver] weapon if it wasn't already.</span></p></li><li><p>Alternatively, you can bless a pound of water, which becomes @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.IndrcQ3rdMXvfyVh]{holy water}. If you use this spell to create holy water, the duration is permanent.</p></li></ul>",
            "chat": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 10 Minutes</p></div><p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require 0.2 pounds of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.fnmCUzOkiNZDOpQ0]{pure holy silver and iron powder} (one quarter sterling silver, three quarters iron), typically valued at 25 gold. You can alternatively use a pound of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.IndrcQ3rdMXvfyVh]{holy water} to sanctify a weapon. This spell consumes this material.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong>Enchant Item</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">You touch a weapon. That weapon counts as a &amp;reference[silver] weapon if it wasn't already.</span></p></li><li><p>Alternatively, you can bless a pound of water, which becomes @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.IndrcQ3rdMXvfyVh]{holy water}. If you use this spell to create holy water, the duration is permanent.</p></li></ul>"
        },
